: {"text": "125 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/66774095"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCDE4OTM3MjgxIKejls8FMAA4rQJAEHIINjY3NzQwOTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1778918784.220606", "card_id": "Q_2038307987094249499", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "余承东称「尊界 s800」4 月上险量超 1100 台，累计交付超 17000 台，真实情况如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 14 日，华为常务董事、产品投资评审委员会主任、终端 BG 董事长余承东发文称，尊界 S8004 月上险量超 1100 台，累计交付超 17000 台。 余承东：尊界 s800 4 月上险量超 1100 台，累计交付超 17"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "115 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038307987094249499"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExOTUwNjYwNyCeqJbQBjAAOB5AEXITMjAzODMwNzk4NzA5NDI0OTQ5OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1778918784.221101", "card_id": "Q_2038632500457465782", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "鸿蒙智行智界 V9 上市，售价 38.98-51.98 万，有哪些技术亮点？预计销量如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8bd1d4472c1cd480951b47b1e266ee21_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "101 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038632500457465782"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExOTUxODIxNiDYhJvQBjAAOCVAEnITMjAzODYzMjUwMDQ1NzQ2NTc4MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1778918784.221558", "card_id": "Q_2036084258695901324", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "律师声称原创内容被央视网抄袭，连刻意埋下的瑕疵表达一并抄走，算侵权吗？作者沟通无果，是不是只能忍了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一、不敢相信自己的眼睛 1. 刚代理完一起 AI 侵权案，我接受媒体新榜采访，就 AI 配音话题发表了法律评论意见，刊在新榜公众号文章《被 AI「偷走」声音？一线配音演员集体向 AI 侵权宣战？》里。没过多久，我看到央视网也做了一期同样选题的报道《配音…AI，…版权…？》。我第一反应还挺高兴的，认为自己还挺有新闻触觉。 2. 但越读越不对劲，直到我把央视网的文章逐字扒完，得出了一个让我难以置信的结论：我的原创内容被抄袭了。不多说，把比对结果放出来： （央视网文章（左）、我的原创内容（右）） （更直观的「调色盘」抄袭比对） 3. 或许有人会反驳：「大家都在聊同一个话题，观点难免雷同，凭什么说人家央视抄你？」 4. 一开始我也不大敢相信堂堂央视会干这种事，毕竟一个国家级权威媒体。我还特意去问了新榜的编辑老师，得到的答复是：新榜也没有授权央视网使用我的原创内容。而且我通常与媒体的合作形式都是独家采访，也不可能同意合作媒体随意授权他人，如此改头换面地使用我的内容啊。 （新榜老师回复确认未授权） 二、我的原创，自带防伪 虽然被改头换面，但其实我的原创内容里，都有大量「防伪标签」，只要遭遇别人抄袭，就会像考试被同桌抄袭那样，把我试卷上的错题、甚至连名带姓一并抄了过去。随便举几个例子： 1. 中文语病表达：「已大量开源」——属于非常规表达，常见说法应为「已大量处于开源阶段」，我当初写的时候，还特意去全网搜了一下，确定没有前人使用过「已大量开源」这样的表述，才刻意使用这种「带病表达」的，没关系，读者能看懂就行。 不管他们怎么删，他们绝对没有想到，还有其他这么多「雷同之处」。更没想到我这种「故意埋雷」的写作技巧——其实我在 2019 年 7 月 5 日写过一篇文章我被抄袭了，对方是央视 央视报道被 AI「偷走」声音？一线配音演员集体向 AI 侵权宣战"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0444906ce74063675f9f9c711c2cd0eb_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2036084258695901324"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExOTQyNjc2NCCb+vXPBjAAOHNAE3ITMjAzNjA4NDI1ODY5NTkwMTMyNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1778918784.223501", "card_id": "Q_2009245585287439261", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《雍正王朝》中，如果最后年羹饶稍微服个软给雍正个台阶是不是就没事了？这个是不是个强行的剧情杀？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a92fe3907218e618b5fa36208c93af21_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2009245585287439261"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExODUxNDY2OSCls+/MBjAAODJAFHITMjAwOTI0NTU4NTI4NzQzOTI2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1778918784.223869", "card_id": "Q_2037684043257472040", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全球昆虫正在以惊人速度灭绝，这会对地球生态系统带来哪些连锁影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "全球昆虫正在以惊人速度灭绝"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-16b95761d51f240d9b7ac1468eff8e5c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037684043257472040"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExOTQ4NDMyOSCGno3QBjAAOGVAFXITMjAzNzY4NDA0MzI1NzQ3MjA0MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1778918784.224391", "card_id": "Q_2036455641170932765", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 61}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "理想 CEO 称「汽车不能像手机一样换代」，如何看待他的观点？现在合理的汽车换代周期到底应该是多久？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 9 日，针对外界关于全新理想 L9 Livis「四年换代周期过长」的讨论，理想汽车 CEO 李想发文回应，直言汽车产业的研发与验证节奏无法向手机看齐。 他表示，汽车关乎一家人的生命安全，从设计到量产需经过大量严苛测试，反复验证、打磨每一个细节。「以媒体拆车为例，这只是车企的‘基本操作’。」他透露，团队会大量拆解理想 L9 路测车，反复核对是否符合设计标定。而要获得数量充足、里程够长、工况复杂的高价值路测车，本身就需要投入大量时间。 对于 AI 技术在汽车测试领域的应用，他也明确指出，尽管 AI 能力强大，但在实车验证环节，对效率的提升「仍然有限」，无法替代真实的道路测试与物理验证流程。 理想汽车 CEO 回应换代周期质疑：汽车不是手机，安全验证无法提速 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dc290b7ca043fe28f4be53f1add97416_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2036455641170932765"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExOTQ0MDc5OSD8rfvPBjAAOGJAFnITMjAzNjQ1NTY0MTE3MDkzMjc2NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1778918784.225200", "card_id": "Q_1906626899117048894", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "经常做运动是不是会比同龄人更显年轻呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "大家都知道做运动有益于身心健康，不仅仅身体得到锻炼可以延缓衰老，心理上也能得到释放，那是不是同一年的人经常做运动和不做运动的人是不是显得更年轻一些呢？，"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f7e50b4b9e672d275a0abfd726778557_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1906626899117048894"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExNDk2MDY5MiCMjZrBBjAAOFJAF3ITMTkwNjYyNjg5OTExNzA0ODg5NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1778918784.225702", "card_id": "Q_1957080618014873079", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些古诗词的内容理解方面存在争议？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7606f9fe62d6ea696d68074471b1ba66_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1957080618014873079"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExNjgwNzk0NCC8pvjGBjAAODdAGHITMTk1NzA4MDYxODAxNDg3MzA3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1778918784.225962", "card_id": "Q_7349267991", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "现在的小女孩为什么很少有戴发箍的了，原因是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我印象中，我是 00 年的，我那上小学，初中那时候，无论是身边的女同学还是同年龄段的女孩，那时候貌似都很喜欢扎马尾，头上戴发箍，看着也是很漂亮，而且五花八门的都有，尤其是很多喜欢带白色的，黑色的，粉色的，各种各样的都有。而且很多小女孩那个时候基本上都是天天戴发箍。 不过貌似在我 2015 年上了高中之后，生活当中就看到小学生初中生的小女孩很少有戴发箍的了，而且还是一年比一年少，到了快 2025 年了，我看现在的小女孩基本上没有戴发箍的了，反正在我这里是这样的，不知道别的地方怎么样... 而且发箍感觉以前只有小学生和初中生喜欢戴，到了上高中年龄大了基本上看不到了 所以说，现在上学的小女孩为什么很少有戴发箍的了？原因是什么呀？还有女孩年龄大了，为什么就不喜欢戴发箍了？原因是什么呀？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-648a252e4dfde083bfbdd6c297906ab8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7349267991"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExMjQ0NjU1MiDzjpO7BjAAOMIBQBlyCjczNDkyNjc5OTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1778918784.226711", "card_id": "Q_2038227376438342670", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "付巧妹团队再发 Nature ，从牙齿化石中获得中国直立人遗传特征，如何理解这一研究的意义？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2026 年 5 月 13 日，中国科学院古脊椎动物与古人类研究所付巧妹团队在 Nature 在线发表题为「Enamel proteins from six Homo erectus specimens across China」的研究论文，该研究首次成功从距今约 40 万年前的中国直立人牙齿化石中提取并分析了蛋白质，不仅鉴定出他们特有的「分子身份证」，更发现了他们可能与另一支神秘古人类——丹尼索瓦人——存在基因交流的关键线索。 《中国六具直立人标本的牙釉质蛋白》 原文摘要： 在非洲、欧亚大陆和东南亚均发现了直立人遗骸 <sup>1,2,3</sup>，其年代可追溯至约两百万年前；然而，由于年代久远且保存状况不佳，从中获取有价值的分子数据一直是一项挑战。本研究成功提取并分析了来自周口店、和县和孙家洞遗址的五具男性和一具女性中更新世直立人标本的古代牙釉质蛋白，这些标本距今约 40 万年。所有三个遗址的标本均具有两个共同的氨基酸变异。其中，AMBN 基因中的 A253G 变异此前未知，也未在其他人类谱系中发现，包括来自格鲁吉亚德马尼西的直立人、来自西班牙阿塔普埃尔卡的先驱人、丹尼索瓦人、尼安德特人和现代人。另一种变异体 AMBN(M273V) 此前已在丹尼索瓦人中发现，而我们现在的证据表明，它可能是通过与中更新世直立人相关的群体引入的。丹尼索瓦人基因组中归因于超古老基因渗入的区域，其中一些后来遗传给了现代人类，很可能起源于直立人。中更新世晚期的直立人可能与丹尼索瓦人在东亚部分地区共存，这些互动被认为就发生在这些地区。 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c073b9e1a1b3273cdafc4a88165d9d5c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038227376438342670"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTExOTUwMzI0MiCKkpXQBjAAOG1AGnITMjAzODIyNzM3NjQzODM0MjY3MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1778918784.227861", "card_id": "Q_427364036", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 501}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么都在说要保护传统手艺，难道不应该让这些落后的东西去直面时代的淘汰？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9699c98f19d62a85d53898947ea14bb8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/427364036"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCDU3MjQ4OTE5IM3m1vwFMAA4sgpAG3IJNDI3MzY0MDM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1778918784.228145", "card_id": "Q_656393238", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么《情满四合院》有那么多的同人文？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-fa1ff0a35b2add06806360a99e789cd9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656393238"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq/K1jfultb4OEAMaCTEwODE0MjkwOSDB2qCyBjAAOG9AHHIJNjU2MzkzMjM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1778918784.228526", "card_id": "Q_2037259013860087102", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果黄仁勋愿